      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THE VICAR OF DIBLEY NZ (3) has not raced for ten weeks but looks forward enough for the return after a minor placing in a recent trial. Ended her last campaign in Sydney but came from wider for second the last time she raced here, A nice draw should ensure a cosy run and she usually goes well fresh. SWEET MIA NZ (4) has been competitive of late. Missed narrowly from the back row two back then came from wider than this when midfield last week. Could take care of this line-up. ZAHRA LOU (8) draws for a trail and has to come into calculations following a string of top-four results. CHEER LEADER (10) must be considered having placed last week and won from this barrier prior.",
